Deprecated API

Contents

  • Deprecated Methods
  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    io.iron.ironmq.Queue.addSubscribersToQueue(ArrayList)
    Use updateSubscribers instead
    io.iron.ironmq.Queue.get()
    Use Queue.reserve() instead
    io.iron.ironmq.Queue.get(int)
    Use Queue.reserve(int) instead
    io.iron.ironmq.Queue.get(int, int)
    Use Queue.reserve(int, int) instead
    io.iron.ironmq.Queues.getAllQueues()
    Deprecated because of two reasons: It doesn't retrieve all queues and Queues.getQueues is more preferable.
    io.iron.ironmq.QueueModel.getErrorQueue()
    io.iron.ironmq.QueueModel.getProject_id()
    Use getProjectId() instead.
    io.iron.ironmq.QueueModel.getPushType()
    io.iron.ironmq.QueueModel.getRetries()
    io.iron.ironmq.QueueModel.getRetriesDelay()
    io.iron.ironmq.QueueModel.getTotal_messages()
    Use getTotalMessages() instead.
    io.iron.ironmq.Queue.releaseMessage(String, int)
    Reservation Id is required for message releasing since v3
    io.iron.ironmq.QueueModel.setErrorQueue(String)
    io.iron.ironmq.QueueModel.setProject_id(String)
    io.iron.ironmq.QueueModel.setPushType(String)
    io.iron.ironmq.QueueModel.setRetries(int)
    io.iron.ironmq.QueueModel.setRetriesDelay(int)
    io.iron.ironmq.QueueModel.setSubscribers(ArrayList)
    io.iron.ironmq.QueueModel.setTotal_messages(int)
    io.iron.ironmq.Queue.touchMessage(String)
    It's not possible to touch a message without reservation id since v3 of IronMQ
